Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.69,0:02:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芥…芥瑚小姐  這是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是虛海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虛海?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,景麒先生和杉本同學他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,台輔和您的朋友在遠方飛著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為台輔很討厭血的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果您覺得冷  請用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請握著劍鞘帶著的這顆寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體開始熱起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這顆碧雙珠能保護您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請千萬不要丟失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是合柚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芥瑚小姐  我們能逃走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您抓好  我去擋住合柚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芥…芥瑚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是伏兵  請趕快用劍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣冗祐無法行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是討厭的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部…都是夢就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明從天上掉下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻一點事都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,景…景麒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…被救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,景麒先生  不來接我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼…這海…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒見過這樣的海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:06:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…可沒見過這樣的海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  誰來救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快讓我回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何  請您隨我來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不離御前  誓約忠誠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您是我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護您  只有請您跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找都不來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不全是你的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有村莊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是日本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的  還哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是來過颱風了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是從海那邊來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡果然還是日本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這把劍怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是別人給的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個叫做景麒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問  景麒是這裡的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把劍交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼玩意兒  原來是裝飾品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請鬆手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:09:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正那把劍只是個擺設而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請別靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是海客  殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首都裡是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是他們把我們的土地搞得一塌糊塗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手  冗祐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冗祐  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你這個海客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到竟然還有海客
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我  這是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請…請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杉…杉本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還以為見不到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也被抓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過  你能活著就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡到底是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來是相當偏僻的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊  杉本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  讓你捲入了這麼奇怪的事件裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:12:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這面鏡子怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照出來的樣子和我不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是普通的鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那不是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是中嵨同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是中嵨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中嵨陽子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲音確實很像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制服也一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的  我是中嵨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣連媽媽…也認不出我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回不了家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那個叫景麒的  說你是他的主人?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想一定是哪裡搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我吃了這麼多的苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連我的臉都變了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是他的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許有什麼事弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定  他找錯主人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…一定會想辦法讓咱們回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為這是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看見了那個奇怪的海了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是另一個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是  村裡的人都說著日語
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是些奇怪的語言嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的語言?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.57,0:14:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到的  確實是日語啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到景麒那兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聲音是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有點不祥的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,景麒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.02,0:15:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡往前走就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  到現在還好意思這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險的事已經夠多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:16:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你誘拐陽子有什麼目的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陽子?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是她的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,景…景麒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問  我們現在會被怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別多問  快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中嵨同學  剛才你說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼能和那個人說話的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是日語啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在用些莫名其妙的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是中國嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中國? 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是個不知位於何方  傳說中的國家的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說這裡不是中國
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你會說這裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不懂海客的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是巧國的配浪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是這裡的閭胥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}閭胥: 裡的長老
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道有這種國家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是從日本來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要把我們關起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海客要交給縣官是規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海客?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從海那邊來的人我們都這麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虛海的東面有一個叫日本的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那裡通過蝕漂流至此的人  就叫海客
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像你們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蝕?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像暴風雨一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大部分海客都會死掉  不過你們運氣好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人不可能穿過虛海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算能來  也不能過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是  景麒是從這裡過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:18:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該有回去的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們會被送到縣廳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡由上面的人決定怎樣處置你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在日本有我的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…想回家…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中…中嵨同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼多人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要和海客在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問  到了縣廳後  我們會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走運的話大概是坐牢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不走運的話是死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死刑?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們要被判死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.84,0:20:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們是壞海客
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王說海客是招來災難的侵略者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道前天有多少莊稼被埋到了泥裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,配浪今年的收成全毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要逃的話  現在可是機會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行的  這樣做的話  真的會被殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:21:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們和上面的人提起景麒的話  一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是…你們在等什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又抓到一個海客
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還以為見不到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淺野君…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說…知道這是什麼地方了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們要遭這種罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一言難盡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過  還好淺野君沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說來  倒是有點像陽子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是有點怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是  為什麼只有陽子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來這兒之後奇妙的事是一件接著一件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相貌變了也算不了什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淺野君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:21:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:21:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了日本就一定能復原了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.06,0:22:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  我在樹林裡遇到景麒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  說過了不准說話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅頭髮的  讓那個多嘴的小子閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,景麒…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,景麒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.87,0:22:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.28,0:22:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  請停車
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,林子裡有我認識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.29,0:22:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.61,0:22:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的  我沒說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嬰…嬰兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.13,0:22:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天在森林裡也聽到過同樣的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.31,0:22:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出…出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野…野狗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.81,0:22:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  那是妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  海客果然是會招來禍患
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.82,0:22:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.03,0:23:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑得好快  要被追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,景麒  你在附近是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.91,0:23:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,景麒…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.93,0:23:29.11,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}月影下無論多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:34.63,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也有虛海無限延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:40.42,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}沉浸在銀色的溫柔中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.66,0:23:45.98,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在開始睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.16,0:23:51.70,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在記憶中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.85,0:23:57.17,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直尋找著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.33,0:24:02.71,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}人的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.88,0:24:07.35,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在孤獨的雨中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.48,0:24:13.14,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使軀體消亡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.31,0:24:18.86,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也一定跑到終點
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.02,0:24:24.53,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直到那個世界的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.70,0:24:30.08,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}到達彩虹為止
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.38,0:24:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛的話  只要一瞬間就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.40,0:24:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這句話重重地壓在胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.02,0:24:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣都難以忘記
